===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Phoebe (Masters)}}
Phoebe forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Dusclops}} and its evolved form {{p|Dusknoir}}, along with {{p|Cofagrigus}} and {{p|Sableye}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Phoebe became a playable sync pair since the game's release.

Phoebe has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[PML arc]]. 

